# SmartCare Wound API Tests
# Use REST Client extension in VS Code to run these requests

### =====================================================
### INFECTION PREDICTION TESTS
### =====================================================

### Test Infection Prediction - Normal Wound Condition (Expected: No Infection)
# Parameters indicate normal healing process
POST http://localhost:5000/predict/infection
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Wound Temperature": 37.2,
    "Wound pH": 7.1,
    "Moisture Level": 70.5,
    "Drug Release": 15.3
}

