### =====================================================
### HEALING TIME PREDICTION TESTS
### =====================================================

### Test Healing Prediction - Minor Wound (Expected: Fast Healing)
# Parameters indicate quick healing time
POST http://localhost:5000/predict/healing
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Wound Type": "Abrasion",
    "Location": "Forearm",
    "Severity": "Mild",
    "Infected": "No",
    "Patient Age": 25,
    "Size": 4.8,
    "Treatment": "Standard Dressing"
}

### Test Healing Prediction - Moderate Wound (Expected: Medium Healing Time)
# Parameters indicate average healing time
POST http://localhost:5000/predict/healing
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Wound Type": "Laceration",
    "Location": "Leg",
    "Severity": "Moderate",
    "Infected": "No",
    "Patient Age": 42,
    "Size": 12.5,
    "Treatment": "Sutures"
}

